roof's 7/7 tests passed against the changed live value while the old hand-transcribed proof failed exactly as predicted -- out_of_range_sample_rate_parses_but_fails_validate panicked on its hardcoded sample_rate=1.5 probe (\"validate() must reject sample_rate=1.5 against stp:minValue=0.0/stp:maxValue=1.0\"), now in-range under the live [0,2] bound. ontology.ttl confirmed reverted byte-for-byte to maxValue=1.0 (git diff empty) and resynced; all 15 tests green again, working tree clean." ;
